## Full Setup Procedure (What We Did)

### Phase 0 — YouTube Setup

1. YouTube Studio → Outside Inn channel → Manage → Schedule Stream
2. Title: `Outside Inn Radio` | Category: Music | Privacy: Public
3. Customization page: left all defaults
4. Visibility page: Public, date/time irrelevant
5. On stream dashboard: scrolled to Additional Settings → **Enable Auto-start: ON**, Auto-stop: OFF
6. Stream key dropdown → Create new stream key → Name: `Outside Inn Radio`, Protocol: RTMP, no manual resolution settings
7. Copied stream key: `qvv0-8ugj-3hy0-66f5-9vgg`

### Phase 1 — Asset Validation (Windows PowerShell)

```powershell
# Video stream check
ffprobe -v error -show_streams -select_streams v:0 D:\StreamSourceFiles\HoldtLoop.mp4

# Audio stream check
ffprobe -v error -show_streams -select_streams a:0 D:\StreamSourceFiles\HoldtLoop.mp4

# Keyframe interval check
ffprobe -v error -select_streams v:0 -show_frames -show_entries frame=pict_type,pts_time -of csv D:\StreamSourceFiles\HoldtLoop.mp4 | Select-String "I" | Select-Object -First 5
```

All passed. Keyframes confirmed at 0, 2, 4, 6, 8 seconds exactly.

### Phase 2 — VPS Cleanup

```bash
ssh root@138.197.9.139
pkill ffmpeg
tmux kill-server
ps aux | grep ffmpeg
# Confirmed: only grep line returned, nothing running
```

### Phase 3 — Upload Video File (Windows PowerShell)

```powershell
scp D:\StreamSourceFiles\HoldtLoop.mp4 root@138.197.9.139:/root/HoldtLoop.mp4
# Transfer: 2.3GB at ~124KB/s, took ~5 hours from Athens
```

Confirmed on VPS:
```bash
ls -lh /root/HoldtLoop.mp4
# -rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2.3G Mar 27 00:28 /root/HoldtLoop.mp4
```

### Phase 4 — Create Environment File

```bash
nano /etc/outside-inn-radio.env
# Typed:
# YT_INGEST_URL=rtmps://a.rtmps.youtube.com/live2
# YT_STREAM_KEY=qvv0-8ugj-3hy0-66f5-9vgg
# Ctrl+O, Enter, Ctrl+X

chmod 600 /etc/outside-inn-radio.env
```

### Phase 5 — Create Systemd Service

```bash
cat > /etc/systemd/system/outside-inn-radio.service << 'EOF'
[Unit]
Description=Outside Inn 24/7 Lo-Fi Radio
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target
StartLimitIntervalSec=600
StartLimitBurst=10

[Service]
Type=simple
EnvironmentFile=/etc/outside-inn-radio.env
ExecStartPre=/usr/bin/test -r /root/HoldtLoop.mp4
ExecStart=/usr/bin/ffmpeg -nostdin -hide_banner -loglevel warning -nostats -re -stream_loop -1 -i /root/HoldtLoop.mp4 -c:v copy -c:a copy -flvflags no_duration_filesize -f flv ${YT_INGEST_URL}/${YT_STREAM_KEY}
Restart=always
RestartSec=5
RestartSteps=5
RestartMaxDelaySec=60
StandardOutput=journal
StandardError=journal

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
EOF
```

### Phase 6 — Enable and Start

```bash
systemctl daemon-reload
systemctl enable outside-inn-radio
# Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/multi-user.target.wants/outside-inn-radio.service

systemctl start outside-inn-radio
systemctl status outside-inn-radio
# Active: active (running) since Fri 2026-03-27 08:03:29 UTC
```

### Verification

YouTube Studio → Outside Inn → Stream health tab:
- Status: **Excellent** ✅
- Message: "Stream is healthy. Stream health is excellent." ✅

