## Daily Operations

### Check if radio is running
```bash
ssh root@138.197.9.139
systemctl status outside-inn-radio
```
`Active: active (running)` = running. That's the whole check.

### View live logs
```bash
journalctl -u outside-inn-radio -f
```
Press `Ctrl+C` to exit — stream keeps running.

### Stop the radio
```bash
systemctl stop outside-inn-radio
```

### Start after a manual stop
```bash
systemctl start outside-inn-radio
```

### Restart (after updating stream key or video file)
```bash
systemctl restart outside-inn-radio
```

