## Key Context

- This radio is separate from the E.I. Werner channel (`@EIWerner`) which is used for live streams
- E.I. Werner live streams go direct to YouTube via OBS on the AERO X16 laptop — no Restream
- The old E.I. Werner lo-fi radio used Restream + tmux — this Outside Inn setup replaces that pattern with direct YouTube + systemd
- The previous 151-hour broadcast on E.I. Werner failed because Restream dropped the VPS connection with no auto-restart — this setup solves both problems
- Mac Mini M4 upgrade (~$499) is deferred — planned post-Athens once streaming cadence is validated

